docs.text: Introduction This documentation summarises various machine learning techniques in Python. They cover only classical modelling. I cover neural network model in another website (WIP). Other aspects of modelling like model deployment & testing are collated in my AI Engineering site. A lot of the content are compiled from various resources, so please cite them appropriately if you are using.
